comment: Snell's (CHI) contact is incidental and does not affect Jackson's (DET) shooting movement.
Noah (CHI) makes incidental contact with Drummond (DET) that does not affect his ability to go for the rebound.
Jackson (DET) does not beat Butler (CHI) to the spot (point of contact) before he starts his upward shooting motion.
Drummond (DET) is in a legal guarding position on the shot attempt by Gasol (CHI).
Jackson (DET) reaches in and makes contact with Mirotic's (CHI) face on the play to the basket.
Gasol (CHI) makes contact with Drummond's (DET) arm and the contact affects his shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (DET) is in a legal guarding position on the drive to the basket by Butler (CHI).
Gasol (CHI) makes contact with Drummond's (DET) body and the contact affects his shot attempt.
Butler (CHI) commits a take foul on Jackson (DET).
Gasol (CHI) commits a take foul on Jackson (DET).
Drummond's (DET) contact is incidental and does not affect Gasol's (CHI) shooting movement.
McDermott (CHI) commits a take foul on Morris (DET).
Morris (DET) does not push Mirotic (CHI), the contact is incidental.
